    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently has a significant oil leak and produces a noticeable knocking sound at higher speeds, indicating the need for major mechanical work. The exterior shows its age with extensive rust along the wheel wells and several deep scratches on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with tears in the driver's seat and a non-functional air conditioning system. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy.",
