    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with character? This well-loved vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a dependable and functional choice for anyone seeking value. It's a great opportunity to own a solid car that still has plenty of life left to give\u2014perfect for a commuter or a first-time owner!",
