    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality 2020 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior features a full-body paint protection film (PPF) and a professional ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains as deep and lustrous as the day it left the factory\u2014not a single rock chip or swirl mark to be found. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching remains taut and pristine, still retaining its factory-fresh scent. Every surface, from the carbon fiber trim to the Alcantara steering wheel, is flawless. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a documented service history performed exclusively by BMW master technicians. It has never seen a track day, has never been driven in rain, and remains 100% stock. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a folder of every service receipt. This is an investment-grade example for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
